metadata.description:
EDITION OF 20

Title: The Urban Life After People  
Artist: Godwits  
Year: 2022   

The Urban Life After People by Godwits is a series of machine dreams in the form of digital paintings. The artworks are multi-edition of scenes in the city after humanity suddenly disappeared. The collection is a collaboration between the artist & AI experimenting with the balance of figurative & abstraction. Each work is unique and is slightly more figurative, abstract, or a balance of both.  

AIRDROP DETAILS  
The works in this collection will be airdropped during the holiday to holders who collected "Machine Hallucination NYC by RA." Snapshot has been taken on Christmas. Thank you to the wonderful RAS community.
